high_descs: Turn left move then turn right and walked to the bathtub.
Pick up the mango from the bath tub.
Turn left move one step then turn left move and turn left to the sink.
Put the mango in the sink, rinse it off, and pick it back up.
Turn around, move one step then turn around and head to the sink.
Put the mango into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the clean Mango into the Sink

high_descs: Turn left then turn right to the bathtub.
Take the mango from the bathtub.
Turn around to the sink side.
Put the mango in the sink, pour the water and take it back.
Turn around and turn back to the sink.
Put the mango in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Take the Mango from the bathtub and Place it in the Sink

high_descs: Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the bathtub
Pick up mango from the bathtub
Turn right and go straight and make a right turn near sink
Place mango inside the fridge and then take it out
Go straight towards the wall and then walk straight into the room, turning to the sink on your right
anns.task_desc: Washing mango on the sink and placing it on sink
